# hard problem

are human hardwired for negativity? 
  
- like to control, power..
- dont like other to succeed..
- dont like to listen..
- lack of objectivity, biases ..
- lack empathy, sympathy..
- dont want to invest in future..
- scared of failure..
- dwell in dark thoughts
- reforming self..
- instantaneous result..
- lack of feedback..
- impress, why..
- saggregation culture, class, food, ethnic..
- suppress other and not empowering other..
- distrust..
- envy..
- dependency..
- resentment..
- stubborn..
- shortsighted..
- resist change..
- ripple effect..
- uncertainity..
- one pulse, one goal, long haul..
